Package: svgedit
Title: Edit SVG files in R to insert ggplot2 plots and text
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Thedie", , "daniel.thedie@ed.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to edit SVG files byt replacing manually-created placeholders (e.g. a rectangle element) by ggplot2 plots or text elements. This allows creating reproducible, automated figures from R code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: 
    xml2,
    ggplot2,
    svglite
Suggests: 
    palmerpenguins,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
